               <picture>\n                  <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/fv_copy05_sp.png\">\n                  <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/fv_copy05.png\" alt=\"電気と暮らしをつなぐ。それが、私たちの使命。\">\n                </picture>\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"copy_img copy06\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/fv_copy06.png\" alt=\"電気と暮らしをつなぐ。それが、私たちの使命。\">\n              </span>\n            </span>\n          </h1>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"message\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n          <svg class=\"message_line01 -pc\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 940.5 1677.9\">\n            <defs>\n              <style>\n                .cls-1 {\n                  fill: none;\n                  stroke: #ef846c;\n                  stroke-miterlimit: 10;\n                  stroke-width: 2px;\n                }\n              </style>\n            </defs>\n            <path class=\"cls-1\" d=\"M405.4.3C357.2,141.3,220.8,250.6,16.3,335.4c282.7,105.6,570.6,127,863.2,75.5C603.1,568.3,312.6,651.4,3.9,637.8c224.7,135.2,529.3,156.6,818.8,47.8,60.6,73.2,110.6,142.6,116.6,239.6,7.2,116.7-146,168.4-286.5,220.8-81.3,30.3-136.8,47.9-178.7,109.8-36.2,58.2-24.6,81.2-23.2,175.6s-11.9,205.5-2.1,246.4\"></path>\n          </svg>\n\n          <svg class=\"message_line01 -sp\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 375.07 1060.18\">\n            <defs>\n              <style>\n                .cls-1 {\n                  fill: none;\n                  stroke: #ef846c;\n                  stroke-miterlimit: 10;\n                  stroke-width: 2px;\n                }\n              </style>\n            </defs>\n            <path class=\"cls-1\" d=\"M158.08.18s-14.56,79.68-133.52,127.39c0,0,112.26,126.08,294.69,126.08,0,0-65.03,185.81-318.19,185.81,0,0,22.37,320.58,321.13,320.58,0,0,99.29,92,23.12,160.04-76.18,68.04-172.41,47.03-172.41,140.09\"></path>\n          </svg>\n\n          <div class=\"message_line02\"></div>\n\n          <picture class=\"message_deco message_deco01\">\n            <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco01_sp.png\">\n            <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco01.png\" alt=\"\">\n          </picture>\n          <picture class=\"message_deco message_deco02\">\n            <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco02_sp.png\">\n            <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco02.png\" alt=\"\">\n          </picture>\n          <picture class=\"message_deco message_deco03\">\n            <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco03_sp.png\">\n            <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco03.png\" alt=\"\">\n          </picture>\n          <picture class=\"message_deco message_deco04\">\n            <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco04_sp.png\">\n            <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_deco04.png\" alt=\"\">\n          </picture>\n          <div class=\"block\">\n            <h2 class=\"lead -fadeUp\">\n              <picture>\n                <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_copy_sp.svg\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/message_copy.svg\" alt=\"電気のあるあたりまえの毎日を守る。\">\n              </picture>\n            </h2>\n            <p class=\"text -fadeUp\">\n              社会生活を営むうえで、<br class=\"-sp\">電気は欠かすことができません。<br>\n              何気なく使っている電化製品やインターネット。<br>\n              ショッピングもレジャーも、働く場所にも。<br>\n              日東工業の使命は、そんな“電気を安全に、<br>あたりまえに使えるようにする”こと。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text -fadeUp\">\n              直接目にすることは少ないかもしれませんが、<br>\n              私たちの製品は、<br class=\"-sp\">世の中のさまざまなところで<br>\n              “あたりまえの毎日を守る”ために<br class=\"-sp\">活躍しています。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text -fadeUp\">\n              しかし電気や通信を守る製品づくりで<br>トップを走り続けている私たちにも、<br>\n              できることは、まだまだあります。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text -fadeUp\">\n              例えば、生活をもっと豊かにする。<br>持続可能な電気の利用や、<br>\n              快適な働き方も追求できると考えています。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text -fadeUp\">\n              例えば、暮らしをもっと安心にする。<br>万が一災害が起きたとき、<br>\n              拡大を防ぐ仕組みをつくり<br class=\"-sp\">社会に貢献できると考えています。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text -fadeUp\">\n              いつでも、電気を安全に使える社会を守るために。<br>\n              私たちと共に電気のこれからを紡いでいきましょう。\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <div class=\"main_container\">\n        <div class=\"repeat_line\"></div>\n        <section class=\"industry\">\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <p class=\"industry_deco -textFlow\">Our Industry</p>\n            <div class=\"cap_group\">\n              <div class=\"cap_index\">\n                <div class=\"cap_index_mask\">\n                  <span class=\"cap_num\"><small>#</small>01</span>\n                  <h3 class=\"cap_jp\">業界を知る</h3>\n                  <span class=\"cap_en\">Our Industry</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"block\">\n              <a class=\"page_link\" href=\"/saiyo/newgraduate/industry/\">\n                <picture class=\"link_img\">\n                  <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/page_industry_sp.jpg\">\n                  <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/page_industry.jpg\" alt=\"電気の流れを知る\">\n                </picture>\n                <div class=\"link_lead\">\n                  <span class=\"txt\">電気の流れを知る</span>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"about\">\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div class=\"cap_group\">\n              <div class=\"cap_index\">\n                <div class=\"cap_index_mask\">\n                  <span class=\"cap_num\"><small>#</small>02</span>\n                  <h3 class=\"cap_jp\">会社・<br class=\"-pc\">事業を知る</h3>\n                  <span class=\"cap_en\">About Us</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"block\">\n              <a class=\"page_link\" href=\"/saiyo/newgraduate/about_strength/\">\n                <picture class=\"link_img\">\n                  <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/page_about_strength_sp.jpg\">\n                  <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/page_about_strength.jpg\" alt=\"日東工業の強み\">\n                </picture>\n                <div class=\"link_lead\">\n                  <span class=\"txt\">日東工業の強み</span>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n              <a class=\"page_link\" href=\"/saiyo/newgraduate/about_data/\">\n                <picture class=\"link_img\">\n                  <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/page_about_data_sp.jpg\">\n                  <img src=\"/saiyo/files/img/newgraduate/top/page_about_data.jpg\" alt=\"数字で見る日東工業\">\n                </picture>\n                <div class=\"link_lead\">\n                  <span class=\"txt\">数字で見る日東工業</span>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"works\">\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div class=\"cap_group\">\n              <div class=\"cap_index\">\n                <div class=\"cap_index_mask\">\n                  <span class=\"cap_num\"><small>#</small>03</span>\n                  <h3 class=\"cap_jp\">仕事を知る</h3>\n                  <span class=\"cap_en\">Works</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </di